h useful planning/domain-agent ideas, then trim unnecessary cross-skill wording, success\n205:- rollout_summaries/2026-06-03T06-09-52-xlov-supergoal_standalone_wording_trim_and_full_surface_check.md (cwd=/Users/danny/Documents/Git/AIDT, rollout_path=/Users/danny/.codex/sessions/2026/06/03/rollout-2026-06-03T15-09-52-019e8c1a-451a-7ac2-a7f7-efbd38d7473b.jsonl, updated_at=2026-06-03T06:30:01+00:00, thread_id=019e8c1a-451a-7ac2-a7f7-efbd38d7473b, useful plan-grounding ideas were kept, then leftover `grill-with-docs`/ADR wording was removed across the active surface)\n209:- supergoal, standalone skill, succinct, grill-with-docs, design-tree grill, CONTEXT.md, ADR, plan grounding, tests/domain-context-contract.test.sh, full surface search\n215:- rollout_summaries/2026-06-03T07-47-15-hgjS-supergoal_korean_learn_label_naturalization_and_commit.md (cwd=/Users/danny/Documents/Git/AIDT, rollout_path=/Users/danny/.codex/sessions/2026/06/03/rollout-2026-06-03T16-47-15-019e8c73-6ed7-7480-b090-05661c6dc988.jsonl, updated_at=2026-06-03T08:00:18+00:00, thread_id=019e8c73-6ed7-7480-b090-05661c6dc988, Korean-facing LEARN labels were naturalized and committed without push)\n219:- supergoal, LEARN, Korean labels, 핵심 용어, 구성 요소, 사용되는 용어, 원자, tests/learn-contract.test.sh, local commit, docs/changelog/changelog-2026-06-03.md\n229:- when the user asked for `업데이트 커밋` after the Korean wording fix -> default to a local commit for `supergoal-skill` unless push is explicitly requested [Task 6]\n233:- `reference/learn.md` is the right load-bearing file for LEARN teaching-flow changes; it now carries the durable bridge sequence `human words -> tiny worked example -> explicit rules -> state/variables -> flow/code -> trace` [Task 1]\n235:- `supergoal` contract tests are literal and wording-sensitive. Safe verification after teaching/contract edits is `./tests/learn-contract.test.sh`, `bash tests/worktree-contract.test.sh`, `bash tests/domain-context-contract.test.sh`, `bash tests/gate-scenarios.test